# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Acadiverse frontend — environment variables (Vite)
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values. `.env` is gitignored.
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Only VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed to the browser bundle. On Vercel, set
# these in the project's Environment Variables settings instead of a .env file.
# See ../DEPLOYMENT.md (Part G) for the full setup.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Backend base URL (no trailing slash). The single axios wrapper reads this.
# Local dev (matches the server's PORT=10000):
VITE_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:10000
# Production example:
# VITE_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com
